node.text:
At-Home & No equipment needed - Let me know how the workout goes!! Get up & get moving today! 💪🏼👏🏼 EMOM 20 min 
Min. 0-1: 10 Squat To RDL To Jump Out 
1-2: 10 Lateral Walks (knees barley off the ground) 5 each way to 6 toe taps 
2-3: 10 each side Side Plank Twist 
3-4: 6 Clams Each Side 
4-5: 12 Squats & Lunge Jumps 
5-6: 10 each way Superman Circles 10 Normal
X3 
Last 2 min.
1 Min. Hold a squat 
1 Min. Hold a plank

node.text:
No equipment needed, currently still sore from this, soooo GOODLUCK! 💪🏼
You will need to turn your phone sideways to get the full view! 
Let me know how you guys like this follow along style & how you like the workout 🔥👏🏼😁
•••••
The Workout to Follow Along:
30 Sec. Jumping Jacks 
30 Sec. Squats 
1 Min. Lunges Forward/Backward (30 Sec. Each Leg)
1 Min. Walk Out-Push Up-Jump-Broad Jump 
30 Sec. Moving Squat Jumps 
30 Sec. Hamstring Exercise 
30 Sec. Bicycles 
30 Sec. Reverse Crunches 
Repeat X3
